    "description": "Shuffled Words is a casual word guessing game!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe have these topics at the moment:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n1980's Movies<br />\r\n1990's Movies<br />\r\n2000 Movies<br />\r\n1980's Songs<br />\r\n1990's Songs<br />\r\nTv Series<br />\r\nAnimes<br />\r\nPlaystation 1 Games<br />\r\nPlaystation 2 Games<br />\r\nXbox Games<br />\r\nSuper Nintendo Games<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEach topic have at least 100 words for you to guess, they're presented randomly at each guess / skip.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou can play by guessing the word, using HINTS, shuffling as many times you like, ordering the word from A to Z, revealing a random word.<br />\r\nNo clue of the current word? you can Skip the word for the next one or ~cheat~ by clicking to reveal the current word.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNo loss here, just fun.<br />\r\n---<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhy should I buy this game?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIt's a relaxing game, you'll support my work, for this and future projects!",
